Package Food

Class NutrientTarget

  • java.lang.Object
    • Food.NutrientTarget

  • public class NutrientTarget
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains information about goals for nutrient values as and ADT. Provides an interface to support addition/deletion of nutrients, access of stored goals, and squared error computation for an arbitrary meal.
    Author:
    Wyatt Wismer
